Call the band, it's time to rock!
Samplitude Music Studio 2014 offers
everything you need for professional
music production whether you're at

Bring your music to the next level

audio editing, authentic instruments
a virtual mixing console and a wide

Professional studio tools for single

* Multitrack recordings in 24-bit / 96 kHz
studio quality

* Vandal SE: Bass & guitar amplifier
* essentialFX: Sensational effects for a
professional sound

classic studio effects
* Vintage Organ: Amazing organ sounds from
past
* Vita 2: Sample player with numerous
filters and effects
* Pop Brass: Crystal clear horns
* Electric Piano: Charming electronic keys
* DN-e1: The spectacular high-end
synthesizer
* Auto Mastering: Fully automatic sound
optimization
* Vocal Tune: Easy pitch correction for
vocals
* MIDI functionality: MIDI-Editor &
MIDI-Learn
* BeatBox 2 Plus: Intuitive beat creation
* 64-bit & multicore support
* VST, ReWire and DirectX support
* Mastering Suite 4: The complete mastering
package

SoundCloud and YouTube
